k.eu/voc/writing/lod/9\">scratched\u003C/rs>\n                                    \u003Cp>The text is placed on the outer surface of the wall. The letters have been highlighted with white painting in modern times to make them more legible.\u003C/p>\n                                    \u003Cdamage ana=\"#text_condition.incomplete text_condition.legible\"/>\n                                \u003C/layout>\n                            \u003C/layoutDesc>\n                        \u003C/objectDesc>\n                        \u003ChandDesc>\n                            \u003ChandNote>\n                                \u003C!--  Based on Glyph table: alpha? (first); alpha09 (second); epsilon18; iota01; mu13. -->\n                                \u003Cp>\n                                    Types list:\n                                    \u003Cref target=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Α-type1.html\">Α type1\u003C/ref>\n                                    \u003Cref target=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Α-type1.3.html\">Α type1.3\u003C/ref>\n                                    \u003Cref target=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ι-type1.html\">Ι type1\u003C/ref>\n                                    \u003Cref target=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Μ-type2.html\">Μ type2\u003C/ref>\n                                    \u003Cref target=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Μ-type2.2.html\">Μ type2.2\u003C/ref>\n                                    \u003Cref target=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Μ-type2.2.html\">Μ type2.2\u003C/ref>\n                                \u003C/p>\n                                \u003Clocus from=\"line1\" to=\"line1\">Line 1\u003C/locus>\n                                \u003Cdimensions type=\"letterHeight